<i>noun</i>: 호전적 [호ː전적], 침략 [침냑], 공세 [공ː세], 공격성 [공ː격썽] <br>
<ul>
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>호전적 [호ː전적]</dt><br>
<dd>belligerence; hostility; aggression</dd><br>
<dd>싸우기를 좋아하는 것.</dd><br>
<dd>A state of being inclined to fight.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>침략 [침냑]</dt><br>
<dd>invasion; aggression</dd><br>
<dd>정당한 이유 없이 남의 나라에 쳐들어감.</dd><br>
<dd>An act of aggressively entering another country without a valid reason.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>공세 [공ː세]</dt><br>
<dd>aggression; offensive movement</dd><br>
<dd>적극적으로 공격하거나 행동하는 태도나 모습.</dd><br>
<dd>An attitude or action of someone being very aggressive.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>공격성 [공ː격썽]</dt><br>
<dd>aggression</dd><br>
<dd>상대방에게 공격이나 거친 행동을 잘 하는 성질.</dd><br>
<dd>The quality of being aggressive or belligerent to another.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>